orthcoming album goes “hard,” and it is only right that he unveils the project using a name that matches it. He wrote, “After over 15yrs as minister incredible, I will be retiring the name “MI Abaga” and taking on a new name for my new project bcuz, my new album hard af and it deserves a new name”.  